    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_162_1564-1667",
      "chapterUid": 162,
      "range": "1564-1667",
      "markText": "每个人有自己的表达方式，如果你不喜欢，只能说明不是为你准备的。 你可以不接受，这是一种自由。但不屑和抨击，翻到另外一个世界观，只能说明你的无知和武断。",
      "totalCount": 3668,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25737640&chapterUid=162&rangeStart=1564&rangeEnd=1667",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c66321c07188b9a8c665d4f?chapterUid=162&rangeStart=1564&rangeEnd=1667"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_175_6276-6348",
      "chapterUid": 175,
      "range": "6276-6348",
      "markText": "世事如书，我偏爱你这一句，愿做个逗号，待在你脚边。 但你有自己的朗读者，而我只是个摆渡人",
      "totalCount": 3408,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25737640&chapterUid=175&rangeStart=6276&rangeEnd=6348",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c66321c07188b9a8c665d4f?chapterUid=175&rangeStart=6276&rangeEnd=6348"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_175_7630-7649",
      "chapterUid": 175,
      "range": "7630-7649",
      "markText": "我们都会上岸，阳光万里，路边鲜花开放。",
      "totalCount": 3280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25737640&chapterUid=175&rangeStart=7630&rangeEnd=7649",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c66321c07188b9a8c665d4f?chapterUid=175&rangeStart=7630&rangeEnd=7649"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_155_4774-4849",
      "chapterUid": 155,
      "range": "4774-4849",
      "markText": "一旦下雨，路上就有肮脏和泥泞，每个人都得踩过去。可是，我有一条命，我愿意努力工作，拼命赚钱，要让这个世界的一切苦难和艰涩，从此再也没有办法伤害到她。”",
      "totalCount": 3135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25737640&chapterUid=155&rangeStart=4774&rangeEnd=4849",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c66321c07188b9a8c665d4f?chapterUid=155&rangeStart=4774&rangeEnd=4849"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_159_2032-2105",
      "chapterUid": 159,
      "range": "2032-2105",
      "markText": "不管是人生还是超市，都会重新洗牌的，会调换位置的。 能找到自己想要的东西就好，能买单就好。",
      "totalCount": 2820,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25737640&chapterUid=159&rangeStart=2032&rangeEnd=2105",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c66321c07188b9a8c665d4f?chapterUid=159&rangeStart=2032&rangeEnd=2105"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_153_847-862",
      "chapterUid": 153,
      "range": "847-862",
      "markText": "所有人的坚强，都是柔软生的茧。",
      "totalCount": 2680,
