      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c66321c07188b9a8c665d4f?chapterUid=153&rangeStart=847&rangeEnd=862"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_154_839-884",
      "chapterUid": 154,
      "range": "839-884",
      "markText": "听歌，像私人的时代记录。在你丢弃的陈旧电脑中，曲库反复循环的那首，应该陪伴了最阴冷的时光。",
      "totalCount": 2585,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25737640&chapterUid=154&rangeStart=839&rangeEnd=884",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c66321c07188b9a8c665d4f?chapterUid=154&rangeStart=839&rangeEnd=884"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_158_826-854",
      "chapterUid": 158,
      "range": "826-854",
      "markText": "青春是丛林，是荒原，是阳光炙热的奔跑，是大雨滂沱的伫立。",
      "totalCount": 2475,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25737640&chapterUid=158&rangeStart=826&rangeEnd=854",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c66321c07188b9a8c665d4f?chapterUid=158&rangeStart=826&rangeEnd=854"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_153_385-407",
      "chapterUid": 153,
      "range": "385-407",
      "markText": "我从一些人的世界路过，一些人从我的世界路过。",
      "totalCount": 2422,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25737640&chapterUid=153&rangeStart=385&rangeEnd=407",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c66321c07188b9a8c665d4f?chapterUid=153&rangeStart=385&rangeEnd=407"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_192_3291-3373",
      "chapterUid": 192,
      "range": "3291-3373",
      "markText": "照顾好自己，爱自己才能爱好别人。如果你压抑，痛苦，忧伤，不自由，又怎么可能在心里腾出温暖的房间，让重要的人住在里面。如果一颗心千疮百孔，住在里面的人就会被雨水打湿。",
      "totalCount": 2272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25737640&chapterUid=192&rangeStart=3291&rangeEnd=3373",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c66321c07188b9a8c665d4f?chapterUid=192&rangeStart=3291&rangeEnd=3373"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25737640_168_5944-6013",
      "chapterUid": 168,
      "range": "5944-6013",
      "markText": "美食和风景的意义，不是逃避，不是躲藏，不是获取，不是记录，而是在想象之外的环境里，去改变自己的世界观，从此慢慢改变心中真正觉得重要的东西。",
      "totalCount": 2205,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25737640&chapterUid=168&rangeStart=5944&rangeEnd=6013",
